data.description: This home is a 2 bed, 2 bath gem with an open floor plan. It also features a basement with a secondary living room, kitchenette, bar, full bath, and a built-in Murphy bed for guests. The fenced-in backyard is an oasis with a covered eating area and a cozy fire pit. Don't forget the enclosed front porch and deck! It's the perfect place that provides both indoor and outdoor spaces to enjoy.
